## PR checklist

- [ ] Only `var(--nf-*)` used for color, radius, shadow, easing, duration
- [ ] Display uses `var(--nf-font-display)` (Nu Sans Display); mono owns metadata
- [ ] Radii within the 3-radius system
- [ ] Every `:hover` coordinates ≥ 2 properties
- [ ] `:focus-visible` present
- [ ] Contrast AA verified (including feature card text over scrim)
- [ ] Emphasis via `.nf-page__hero-emph` / `--mute`, not italic or serif
- [ ] No random per-item accents; palette consistent across collection
- [ ] No "hero card" — feature grid is symmetric with overlap-studio rhythm
- [ ] No spotlight fold + grid duplicating CTAs
- [ ] Hero visual uses transparent PNG (srgba 4.0) from `/brand/cards/`; no opaque dark box behind it
- [ ] Feature thumbs have scrim gradient preserved, `opacity: 0.45` baseline
- [ ] Display sizes honor the bold defaults (hero ≥ clamp 56/9vw/128, section ≥ clamp 40/5.8vw/88)
- [ ] Scroll-linked motion present on hero + section titles (parallax, scrub)
- [ ] Cursor-tilt on hero visual
- [ ] Theme toggle minimal
- [ ] No file outside scope touched (prototypes, `prototype.css`, `platform.legacy.css`)
- [ ] `STYLE_GUIDE.md` updated if tokens or patterns changed

